n an option.'=>'您的 AMP slug (%1$s) 定义较晚，很可能通过 %2$s 过滤器或 %3$s 常量在主题中定义。 确保这是在顶级插件中定义的，因此它发生在 %4$s 之前。 虽然后期定义的 AMP slug 仍然可以工作，但需要额外的工作才能通过将其存储在选项中来使 slug 在 WordPress 执行中更早可用。','For best results, the AMP slug (query var) should be available early in WordPress\'s execution flow, specifically before the %s action occurs (at priority 4). This slug is used to construct the paired AMP URLs.'=>'为获得最佳结果，AMP slug（查询变量）应在 WordPress 执行流程的早期可用，特别是在 %s 操作发生之前（优先级为 4）。此 slug 用于构建配对的 AMP URL。','The AMP slug (query var) was defined early'=>'AMP slug（查询变量）定义太早','The AMP slug (query var) was defined late'=>'AMP slug（查询变量）定义太晚','AMP slug (query var) definition timing'=>'AMP slug（查询变量）定义时间','Copy to clipboard'=>'复制到剪贴板','The requested URL is not an AMP page.'=>'请求的 URL 不是 AMP 页面。','The requested URL is not an AMP page. AMP may have been disabled for the URL. If so, you can forget the Validated URL.'=>'请求的 URL 不是 AMP 页面。如果 AMP 被禁用，您可以忘记验证的 URL。','The requested URL did not result in an AMP page being rendered.'=>'请求的 URL 未能呈现 AMP 页面。','View on Instagram'=>'在Instagram上查看','See more'=>'查看更多','The post data could not be successfully retrieved.'=>'无法成功获取文章数据。','Leave review'=>'发表评价','The function was called too early (before the plugins_loaded action) to determine the plugin source.'=>'该函数调用过早（在plugins_loaded动作之前），无法确定插件来源。','WordPress is not currently doing any hook.'=>'WordPress目前没有做任何挂钩操作。','Invalid or missing value for attribute %s'=>'属性值 %s无效或缺失','Mark unreviewed'=>'标为未检查','Mark reviewed'=>'标为已检查','Calling this function before the %1$s action means it will not have access to %2$s and the queried object to determine if it is an AMP response, thus neither the %3$s filter nor the AMP enabled toggle will be considered.'=>'在%1$s操作之前调用此函数意味着该函数将无法访问%2$s和查询的对象来确定它是否是AMP响应，因此将不会考虑%3$s过滤和启用AMP切换。','%1$s (or %2$s, formerly %3$s) was called too early and so it will not work properly.'=>'%1$s （或者 %2$s，以前称为 %3$s）的调用时机过早，因此无法正常工作。','Duplicate dimensions'=>'重复的尺寸','Class name'=>'类名','CSS selector'=>'CS