>WP_DEBUG_DISPLAY</code> 设置为 <code>true</code>），或者查看 PHP 错误日志。 了解有关<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/debugging-in-wordpress/">在 WordPress 中执行调试</a>的更多信息。','Error:'=>'错误：','The AMP enabled status failed to be updated.'=>'AMP启用状态无法更新。','Insufficient permissions to change whether AMP is enabled.'=>'没有足够的权限来更改是否启用AMP。','AMP is not supported for the "%s" post type.'=>'"%s" 文章类型不支持AMP。','This post type is not <a href="%s" target="_blank">enabled</a>.'=>'该文章类型未<a href="%s" target="_blank">启用</a>。','There are no <a href="%s" target="_blank">supported templates</a>.'=>'没有<a href="%s" target="_blank">受支持的模板</a>。','You can import some settings from the primary Active theme into the corresponding Reader theme settings.'=>'您可以将一些设置从激活的主题导入到相应的阅读器主题中。','themeImport'=>'导入','Import settings'=>'导入设置','You are customizing the AMP version of your site. <a href="%s">Customize non-AMP version</a>.'=>'您正在自定义站点的AMP版本。<a href="%s">自定义非AMP版本</a>。','While <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">AMP</a> works well on both desktop and mobile pages, your site is <a href="%2$s" target="_blank">currently configured</a> in Reader mode to serve AMP pages to mobile visitors. These settings customize the experience for these users.'=>'虽然 <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">AMP</a> 在桌面端和移动端页面上均可正常运行，但您的站点<a href="%2$s" target="_blank">当前已配置</a>为阅读器模式，以便为移动端访客提供 AMP 页面。 这些设置可定制这些用户的体验。','Alternatively, you may enable %s to show the error details below.'=>'您还可以启用 %s，以在下面显示错误详细信息。','The error details appear below.'=>'错误详细信息显示在下面。','A PHP fatal error occurred while validating the URL. This may indicate either a bug in theme/plugin code or it may be due to an issue in the AMP plugin itself.'=>'验证 URL 时发生 PHP 致命错误。 这可能表明主题/插件代码中存在错误，也可能是 AMP 插件本身存在问题。','%s issue:'=>'%s 问题：','%s kept'=>'%s 已保留','%s unreviewed'=>'%s 未检查','View with AMP disabled'=>'在禁用 AMP 的情况下查看','Validate URL'=>'已验证URL','Unreviewed'=>'未审阅','The specified layout %1$s is not supported by tag %2$s.'=>'标签 %2$s 不支持指定的布局 %1$s。','The implied layout