dated. To obtain the latest stylesheet information, <a href="%s">recheck this URL</a>.'=>'该URL的样式表信息不再可用。 此类数据一周后会自动删除，以减少占用的数据库存储空间。 由于主题和插件的更新会导致此类数据过时，因此几乎没有长期存储的价值。 要获取最新的样式表信息，请<a href="%s">再次访问该URL</a>。','AMP is disabled because some invalid markup has been kept. To enable AMP to be served, either mark the invalid markup as &#8220;removed&#8221; or provide an AMP-compatible fix that eliminates the invalid markup from being generated in the first place.'=>'AMP已禁用，因为其中保留了一些无效的标记。 要想使此AMP成功加载，请将无效标记标记为&#8220;已移除&#8221;，或者对其进行修复，使其与AMP兼容，以保证最初就不会生成无效标记。','For each instance of invalid markup, determine whether it can be safely removed or it needs to be kept. You can change the Markup Status (Removed or Kept) and click the Preview Changes button to see its impact on the page. Once the proper action has been taken (Remove or Keep), you can toggle the checkbox the instance as Reviewed.'=>'对于无效标记的实例，确定是否可以安全地删除标记或需要保留他们。您可以更改标记状态（已删除或保留），然后单击"预览更改"按钮以查看其对页面的影响。采取正确操作后（删除或保留），您可以将该复选框切换为"已审"。','Invalid markup not reviewed'=>'无效的标记未审核','Plugins have been updated since these results were obtained.'=>'自获得这些结果以来，插件已更新。','The theme has changed since these results were obtained.'=>'在获得这些结果之后，主题已更改。','The theme and plugins have changed since these results were obtained.'=>'自获得这些结果以来，主题和插件已更改。','Location:'=>'位置:','There are no validated URLs with this validation error. Would you like to delete it?'=>'没有带有此验证错误的已验证 URL。 是否要将其删除？','CSS usage not availablen/a'=>'n/a','Confirm that the action being taken on the invalid markup (causing a validation error) has been seen and approved.'=>'确认已查看并批准了对无效标记（导致验证错误的标记）执行的操作。','Reviewed'=>'已审阅','AMP DevTools'=>'AMP开发工具','Redirecting since AMP version not available.'=>'AMP版本不可用，正在重定向。','The AMP plugin no longer allows `amp_supportable_templates` filters to specify a template\'s support as being `immutable`. This is now managed only in AMP Settings.'=>'AMP 插件不再允许 `amp_supportable_templates` 过滤器将模板的支持指定为 `immutable`。 现在只能在 AMP 设置中对其进行管理。','The AMP plugin no longer allows `amp_supportable_templates` filters to specify a template as being `supported`. This is now managed only in AMP Settings.'=>'AMP 插件不再允许 `amp_supportable_templates` 过滤器将模板指定为 `supported`。 现在只能在 AMP 设置中对其进行管理。','AMP Unavailable'=>'AMP不可用','The AMP Reader theme %1$s cannot be found. Your site is currently falling back to using the Legacy templates for AMP pages. Please <a href="%2$s">re-select</a> the desired Reader theme.'=>'找不到AMP阅读器主题 %1$s。 您的站点目前正在回退，以便为 AMP 页面使用旧模板。 请<a href="%2$s">重新选择</a>所需的阅读器主题。','The %s argument is deprecated.'=>'%s 参数已弃用。','Removal of %1$s link should be done by removing %2$s from the %3$s action at %4$s.'=>'%1$s 链接的移除应该通过从 %4$s 的 %3$s 操作中移除 %2$s 来实现。','Filter for "%1$s" added too late. To disable AMP, this filter must be added before the "%2$s" action.'=>'针对“%1$s”的过滤器的添加时机过晚。 要禁用 AMP，必须在执行“%2$s”操作之前添加此过滤器。','prefix for theme card in listReader:'=>'阅读器：','Customize'=>'自定义','This has been <a href="%s">selected</a> as the AMP Reader theme.'=>'已被<a href="%s">选为</a> AMP 阅读器主题。','unreviewed'=>'未审阅','reviewed'=>'已审阅','kept'=>'保持','removed'=>'已移除','Invalid markup causing the validation error is %1$s and %2$s. See all validated URL(s) with this validation error.'=>'导致验证错误的无效标记是“%1$s”和“%2$s”。 查看包含此验证错误的所有已验证 URL。','This link is not applicable in this context. It remains here for preview purposes only.'=>'此链接不适用于该语境， 此处仅保留供预览。','Go to mobile version'=>'转到手机版','Exit mobile version'=>'退出移动版','Sorry, you are not allowed to manage options for the AMP plugin for WordPress.'=>'抱歉，您没有权限管理 WordPress 的 AMP 插件的选项。','Sorry, the current user is not allowed to make this change.'=>'抱歉，不允许当前用户执行此更改。','This presumes you have some experience coding with HTML, CSS, JS, and PHP.'=>'此操作假设您具有 HTML、CSS、JS 和 PHP 的编码经验。','Enable AMP developer tools to surface validation errors when editing posts and viewing the site.'=>'启用 AMP 开发人员工具，以在编辑文章和查看站点时显示验证错误。','AMP Developer Tools'=>'AMP 开发人员工具','Whether the user has enabled dev tools.'=>'用户是否启用了开发工具。','Additionally, AMP requires HTTPS for most components to work properly, including iframes and videos.'=>'此外，AMP 需要使用 HTTPS 才能保证大多数组件（包括 iframe 和视频）正常工作。','Open the onboarding wizard'=>'打开入门向导','Bring the speed and capabilities of the AMP web framework to your site; support content authoring and website development with the effective tools the AMP plugin provides.'=>'为您的站点添加 AMP Web 框架的速度和功能，使用 AMP 插件提供的有效工具支持内容创作和网站开发。','AMP Onboarding Wizard'=>'AMP 入门向导','The original templates included in the plugin with limited customization options.'=>'插件中包含的原始模板所具有的自定义选项有限。','AMP Legacy'=>'AMP Legacy','The operation failed, please reload the page and try again.'=>'操作失败，请重新加载页面并重试。','Reload the page to refresh the diagnostic check.'=>'重新加载页面以刷新诊断检查。','Re-enable transient caching'=>'重新启用瞬态缓存','If you have identified and eliminated the cause of the variable CSS, please re-enable transient caching to reduce the amount of CSS processing required to generate AMP pages.'=>'如果您已确定并消除了导致 CSS 可变的原因，请重新启用瞬态缓存，以减少生成 AMP 页面所需的 CSS 处理量。','On sites which have highly variable CSS and are not using a persistent object cache, the transient caching of parsed stylesheets may be automatically disabled in order to prevent a site from filling up its <code>%1$s</code> table with too many transients. Examples of highly variable CSS include dynamically-generated style rules with selectors referring to user IDs or elements being given randomized background colors. There are two filters which may be used to configure the CSS transient monitoring: <code>%2$s</code> and <code>%3$s</code>.'=>'在具有高度可变 CSS 且不使用持久对象缓存的站点上，可能会自动禁用解析样式表的瞬态缓存，以防止站点用太多的 <code>%1$s</code> 瞬态填充其表。高度可变 CSS 的示例包括动态生成的样式规则，选择器引用用户 ID 或元素被随机化背景颜色。有两个筛选器可用于配置 CSS 瞬态监视： <code>%2$s</code> 和 <code>%3$s</code> 。','Paired Browsing'=>'成对浏览','Calculated time series for monitoring the stylesheet caching'=>'用于监控样式表缓存的计算时间序列','Message'=>'消息','Failed to fetch: %1$s (%2$s)'=>'未能获取：%1$s (%2$s)','AMP Paired Browsing:'=>'AMP配对浏览：','AMP optimization could not be completed due to the following:'=>'由于以下原因，无法完成AMP优化：','URL validation failed due to unexpected JSON in AMP validation response.'=>'由于AMP验证响应中出现意外的JSON，URL 验证失败。','URL validation failed due to the AMP validation request not returning JSON data. This may be due to a PHP fatal error occurring.'=>'由于AMP验证请求未返回JSON数据，此URL验证失败。 原因可能是发生了PHP致命错误。','Unable to validate URL. A white screen of death was encountered which is likely due to a PHP fatal error.'=>'无法验证 URL。 发生了白屏死机，原因可能是出现了PHP致命错误。','Please check your server PHP error logs; to do this you may need to <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">enable</a> %2$s.'=>'请检查您的服务器PHP错误日志；为此，您可能需要<a href="%1$s" target="_blank">启用</a> %2$s。','Too many redirects.'=>'重定向过多。','Nonce authentication failed.'=>'Nonce 身份验证失败。','Preview link expired. Please try again.'=>'预览链接已过期， 请重试。','Required attribute value'=>'必需的属性值','Required ancestor element'=>'必需的上级元素','Disallowed ancestor element'=>'不允许的上级元素','Required parent element'=>'必需的父元素','Required minimum child count'=>'所需的最小子项计数','Required child count'=>'所需的子项计数','Children count'=>'子项计数','First child tag'=>'第一个子标签','Child tag'=>'子标签','Missing attributes'=>'缺少属性','Property value'=>'属性值','Required property value'=>'必需的属性值','Invalid property value'=>'无效的属性值','Property name'=>'属性名称','Missing property'=>'缺失的属性','Mutually exclusive attributes'=>'互斥的属性','Inconsistent units for width and height'=>'宽度和高度所用的单位不一致','Invalid value %1$s for attribute %2$s'=>'属性 %2$s 的值 %1$s 无效','Missing URL for attribute %s'=>'属性缺少 URL %s','The relative URL %1$s for attribute %2$s is disallowed'=>'不允许属性 %2$s 的相对 URL %1$s','Malformed URL %1$s for attribute %2$s'=>'属性 %2$s 的 URL %1$s 格式错误','Invalid URL protocol %1$s for attribute %2$s'=>'属性 %2$s 的 URL 协议 %1$s 无效','The tag %1$s may only appear as a descendant of tag %2$s'=>'标签 %1$s 只能作为标签 %2$s 的后代出现','The tag %1$s may not appear as a descendant of tag %2$s'=>'标签 %1$s 不能作为标签 %2$s 的后代出现','The parent tag of tag %1$s cannot be %2$s'=>'标签 %1$s 的父标签不能为 %2$s','Tag %1$s must have a minimum of %2$s child tag'=>'标签 %1$s 必须至少有 %2$s 个子标签','Tag %1$s must have %2$s child tag'=>'标签 %1$s 必须有 %2$s 个子标签','Tag %1$s is disallowed as first child of tag %2$s'=>'标签 %1$s 不允许作为标签 %2$s 的第一个子标签','Tag %1$s is disallowed as child of tag %2$s'=>'标签 %1$s 不允许作为标签 %2$s 的子标签','Missing at least one mandatory attribute'=>'至少缺少一项必需属性','Missing exclusive mandatory attribute'=>'缺少互斥的必需属性','Mutually exclusive attributes encountered'=>'存在互斥的属性','Missing required attribute'=>'缺少必需属性','Invalid value for %1$s property: %2$s'=>'%1$s 属性的值无效：%2$s','Missing required property'=>'缺少必需属性','Invalid property'=>'无效的属性','Invalid JSON'=>'无效的 JSON','Illegal text content'=>'非法文字内容','Stylesheet fetch error'=>'样式表提取错误','Invalid inline script'=>'无效的内联脚本','Inline Text'=>'内联文本','Inline Type'=>'内联类型','Dependent Style'=>'从属样式','Dependent Script'=>'从属脚本','Enqueued Style'=>'排队样式','Enqueued Script'=>'排队脚本','required value'=>'必需值','Error code'=>'错误代码','Malformed %s characters, possibly incorrectly encoded'=>'%s 字符格式错误，可能是编码错误','Syntax error'=>'语法错误','Control character error, possibly incorrectly encoded'=>'控制字符错误，可能是编码错误','Invalid or malformed JSON'=>'无效或格式错误的 JSON','The maximum stack depth has been exceeded'=>'已超过最大堆栈深度','Expected JSON, got an empty value'=>'JSON符合预期，但值为空','Show styles removed during tree-shaking'=>'显示在摇树优化期间移除的样式','All of the stylesheet was removed during tree-shaking.'=>'摇树优化期间移除了所有样式表。','The stylesheet was empty after minification (removal of comments and whitespace).'=>'经过精简（移除注释和空格）后，样式表为空。','Class name generated during extraction of inline style to style[amp-custom].'=>'将内联样式提取为 style[amp-custom] 时生成的类名称。','Selector generated to increase specificity for important properties so that the CSS cascade is preserved. AMP does not allow important properties.'=>'生成了选择器以提高针对重要属性的专用性，从而保留CSS级联。 AMP不允许使用important 属性。','Selector generated to increase specificity so the cascade is preserved for properties moved from style attribute to CSS rules in style[amp-custom].'=>'生成了选择器以提高专用性，以便对标有 style[amp-custom] 标记从样式属性移到 CSS 规则的属性保留级联。','CSS Code'=>'CSS 代码','Stylesheet URL'=>'样式表URL','Original Markup'=>'原始标记','Stylesheet excluded due to exceeding CSS budget'=>'由于超出CSS预算，样式表已被排除','Stylesheet overruns CSS budget yet it is still included on page'=>'样式表超出了CSS预算，但仍包含在页面中','Stylesheet included'=>'包含的样式表','Stylesheet bytes of total CSS added to page'=>'已添加到页面的总CSS样式表字节数','Expand/collapse'=>'展开/折叠','Markup'=>'标记','Included'=>'包括','Priority'=>'优先级','Percent'=>'百分比','Final'=>'最终','Minified'=>'精简后','Original'=>'原始','Order'=>'排序','You are nearing the limit of the CSS budget. Once this limit is reached, stylesheets deemed of lesser priority will be excluded from the page. Please review the stylesheets below and determine if the current theme or a particular plugin is including excessive CSS.'=>'您已接近 CSS 预算上限。 达到此上限后，页面中优先级较低的样式表将被排除。 请查看下方样式表，确定当前主题或特定插件是否包含过多 CSS。','Please review the flagged stylesheets below and determine if the current theme or a particular plugin is including excessive CSS.'=>'请查看下方标出的样式表，确定当前主题或特定插件是否包含过多 CSS。','You have exceeded the CSS budget. Stylesheets deemed of lesser priority have been excluded from the page.'=>'您已超出 CSS 预算。 优先级较低的样式表已从页面中排除。','You have exceeded the CSS budget. The page will not be served as a valid AMP page.'=>'您已超出 CSS 预算。 该页面将不会作为有效的 AMP 页面。','Excluded minified CSS (%s stylesheet):'=>'已排除且经过精简的 CSS（%s 样式表）：','Percentage of used CSS budget (%sKB):'=>'已使用的 CSS 预算百分比 (%sKB)：','Total CSS size after minification:'=>'精简后的CSS总大小：','abbreviation for bytesB'=>'B','bytes'=>'字节','Total CSS size prior to minification:'=>'精简前的CSS总大小：','Unable to retrieve data for stylesheets.'=>'无法检索样式表的数据。','Stylesheets'=>'样式表','CSS Usage'=>'CSS使用情况','AMP version'=>'AMP版本','Non-AMP version'=>'非AMP版本','Go Back'=>'返回','Exit'=>'退出','The navigated URL is not available for paired browsing.'=>'所导航的URL不可用于成对浏览。','Exit paired browsing onto the AMP version.'=>'退出成对浏览，进入 AMP 版本。','Exit paired browsing onto the non-AMP version.'=>'退出成对浏览，进入非 AMP 版本。','Skip to the AMP iframe'=>'跳转至 AMP iframe','Skip to the non-AMP iframe'=>'跳转至非 AMP iframe','Loading&#8230;'=>'加载中&#8230;','Large site detected. Deactivation will leave orphaned scheduled events behind.'=>'检测到大型站点。 如果停用此项，将会留下孤立的已计划事件。','This option does not apply to Reader mode.'=>'此选项不适用于阅读器模式。','No template supported'=>'没有支持的模板','Number of stylesheet transient cache entries'=>'样式表瞬态缓存条目数','Sampling range for monitoring stylesheet caching'=>'用于监控样式表缓存的采样范围','Threshold for monitoring stylesheet caching'=>'用于监控样式表缓存的阈值','Transient caching for stylesheets disabled'=>'样式表的瞬态缓存已禁用','Serve all templates as AMP?'=>'是否将所有模板用作 AMP？','Templates enabled'=>'已启用模板','Debugging information for the Official AMP Plugin for WordPress.'=>'WordPress 官方 AMP 插件的调试信息。','Your server currently does not have the Xdebug PHP extension loaded'=>'您的服务器当前未加载Xdebug PHP扩展','Please deactivate Xdebug to improve performance. Otherwise, you may enable %s to indicate that this site is currently under development or is undergoing debugging.'=>'请停用 Xdebug 以提高性能。 除此之外，您还可以启用 %s，以表明该站点当前正在开发或正在调试。','Nevertheless, %s is enabled which suggests that this site is currently under development or is undergoing debugging.'=>'但 %s 已启用，表明该站点当前正在开发或正在调试。','Your server currently has the Xdebug PHP extension loaded'=>'您的服务器当前已加载Xdebug PHP扩展','The Xdebug extension can cause some of the AMP plugin&#8217;s processes to time out depending on your system resources and configuration. It should not be enabled on a live site (production environment).'=>'Xdebug 扩展可能导致某些 AMP 插件的进程超时，具体取决于您的系统资源和配置。 不应在正在运行的站点（生产环境）中启用此扩展。','Transient caching of parsed stylesheets is enabled'=>'已解析样式表的瞬态缓存已启用','Transient caching of parsed stylesheets is disabled'=>'已解析样式表的瞬态缓存已禁用','Transient caching of parsed stylesheets is not used due to external object cache'=>'由于启用了外部对象缓存，未使用已解析样式表的瞬态缓存','The version of ICU (v%s) looks good'=>'ICU (v%s) 的版本看起来一切正常','The version of ICU (v%s) is out of date'=>'ICU (v%s) 的版本已过期','The ICU version is unknown, as the constant %s is not defined'=>'未定义常量 %s，ICU 版本未知','Learn more about ICU'=>'了解ICU的更多信息','The version of ICU can affect how the intl extension runs. This extension is used to derive AMP Cache URLs for internationalized domain names (IDNs). The minimum recommended version of ICU is v%s.'=>'ICU 的版本可能会影响 intl 扩展的运行方式。 此扩展用于派生国际化域名 (IDN) 的 AMP 缓存 URL。 推荐使用的最低 ICU 版本是 v%s。','The cURL multi functions are defined'=>'cURL multi函数已定义','The following %1$s cURL multi function is not defined: %2$s.'=>'未定义下列 %1$s cURL 多函数：%2$s。','Learn more about these functions'=>'详细了解这些函数','https://www.php.net/manual/en/book.curl.php'=>'https://www.php.net/manual/en/book.curl.php','The AMP plugin is able to more efficiently determine the dimensions of images lacking width or height by making parallel requests via cURL multi.'=>'AMP插件可以通过cURL multi发出并行请求，从而更有效地确定缺少宽度或高度的图像的尺寸。','(opens in a new tab)'=>'（在新窗口中打开）','Learn more about persistent object caching'=>'了解有关持久对象缓存的更多信息','Xdebug extension'=>'Xdebug 扩展','Transient caching of stylesheets'=>'样式表的瞬态缓存','ICU version'=>'ICU版本','cURL multi functions'=>'cURL multi 函数','Failed to fetch URL to validate.'=>'未能获取用于验证的URL。','Please include your <a href="%s">Site Health Info</a>.'=>'请提供您的<a href="%s">站点健康信息</a>。','Please check your <a href="%s">Site Health</a> to verify it can perform loopback requests.'=>'请检查您的<a href="%s">站点健康</a>，以确保它可以执行环回请求。','If you are stuck, please search the <a href="%1$s">support forum</a> for possible related topics, or otherwise start a <a href="%2$s">new support topic</a> including the error message, the URL to your site, and your active theme/plugins.'=>'如果您遇到了困难，请在<a href="%1$s">支持论坛</a>中搜索可能的相关主题。如果没有找到相关信息，您可以发起<a href="%2$s">新的支持主题</a>，然后在其中添加错误消息、您的站点URL以及您目前采用的主题/插件。','Invalid Markup'=>'无效的标记','CSS property'=>'CSS属性','Illegal CSS !important property'=>'非法的CSS !important属性','Illegal CSS property'=>'非法的CSS属性','CSS parse error'=>'CSS解析错误','Unrecognized CSS'=>'无法识别的CSS','Invalid script'=>'无效的脚本','%s byte'=>'%s 字节','An expected parent was not found. Did you filter %s to not honor the template hierarchy?'=>'找不到预期的父项。 您是否过滤了 %s，以保证不遵循模板层级？','Text content'=>'文本内容','Parent element'=>'父元素','Node name'=>'节点名称','Element name'=>'元素名称','Attribute name'=>'属性名','At-rule'=>'＠规则','Code'=>'代码','Unknown error (%s)'=>'未知错误 (%s)','Duplicate element'=>'重复元素','Invalid processing instruction'=>'无效的处理指令','Custom HTML'=>'自定义HTML','(priority %d)'=>'（优先级 %d）','Core'=>'核心','Must-Use Plugin'=>'强制使用的插件','Plugin'=>'插件','Theme'=>'主题','Action'=>'操作','Filter'=>'筛选','Location'=>'位置','Function'=>'功能','Shortcode'=>'简码','Block Name'=>'区块名称','Block Index'=>'区块索引','Post Type'=>'文章类型','Post ID'=>'文章 ID','Name'=>'名称','Source stack (%s)'=>'源堆栈 (%s)','AMP allows a specific set of elements and attributes on valid AMP pages. Learn about the <a href="%1$s">AMP HTML specification</a>. If an element or attribute is not allowed in AMP, it must be removed for the page to be <a href="%2$s">cached and eligible for prerendering</a>.'=>'AMP允许在有效的AMP页面上使用一组特定的元素和属性。 了解<a href="%1$s">AMP HTML规范</a>。 如果AMP中不允许使用某个元素或属性，则必须将其移除，以保证页面可以<a href="%2$s">得到缓存并符合预呈现的条件</a>。','AMP allows you to <a href="%1$s">style your pages using CSS</a> in much the same way as regular HTML pages, however there are some <a href="%2$s">restrictions</a>. Nevertheless, the AMP plugin automatically inlines external stylesheets, transforms %3$s qualifiers, and uses tree shaking to remove the majority of CSS rules that do not apply to the current page. Nevertheless, AMP does have a 75KB limit and tree shaking cannot always reduce the amount of CSS under this limit; when this happens an excessive CSS error will result.'=>'AMP 允许您使用 <a href="%1$s">CSS 对页面进行样式设置</a> ，其方式与常规 HTML 页面大致相同，但是有一些 <a href="%2$s">限制</a>。AMP 插件会內联外置样式表，转换 %3$s 限定符，并使用树抖动来删除大多数不适用于当前页面的 CSS 规则。然而，AMP有一个75KB的限制，树抖动不能总是减少CSS量到低于这个限制；发生这种情况时，将导致过多的 CSS 错误。','Information'=>'信息','Misc'=>'杂项','Kept'=>'保持','HTML element'=>'HTML 元素','Cleared %s validation error for invalid markup that no longer occurs on the site.'=>'清除了站点上不再发生的无效标记的%s验证错误。','Invalid CSS'=>'无效的CSS','With invalid CSS'=>'带有无效的CSS','Invalid JS'=>'无效的JS','With invalid JS'=>'包含无效的JS','Invalid HTML attributes'=>'无效的HTML属性','With invalid HTML attributes'=>'包含无效的HTML属性','Invalid HTML elements'=>'无效的HTML元素','With invalid HTML elements'=>'包含无效的HTML元素','All types of invalid markup'=>'所有类型的无效标记','Filter by markup status'=>'按标记状态过滤','AMP Validated URL'=>'AMP已验证URL','AMP is enabled because no invalid markup is being kept.'=>'AMP已启用，因为没有保留无效的标记。','Keep'=>'保留','The rechecked URL is free of non-removed invalid markup.'=>'重新检查的URL没有未删除的无效标记。','The rechecked URL still has remaining invalid markup kept.'=>'重新检查的URL仍保留着无效的标记。','Hook: %s'=>'钩子: %s','Excerpt'=>'摘要','Content'=>'内容','Context'=>'上下文','When invalid markup is removed it will not block a URL from being served as AMP; the validation error will be sanitized, where the offending markup is stripped from the response to ensure AMP validity. If invalid AMP markup is kept, then URLs is occurs on will not be served as AMP pages.'=>'移除无效的标记后，它不会再阻止UR 用作AMP，因为验证错误将被清除，这会从响应中删除违规的标记以确保AMP的有效性。 如果保留了无效的AMP标记，则存在无效标记的 URL的页面将不会用作AMP页面。','Markup Status'=>'标记状态','All markup valid'=>'所有标记均有效','Invalid markup removed'=>'无效的标记已删除','%s validation error with removed markup is new'=>'%s 个带有已移除标记的验证错误为新错误','Invalid markup kept'=>'保留无效的标记','%s validation error with kept markup is new'=>'%s 个带有保留标记的验证错误为新错误','https://wordpress.org/support/article/why-should-i-use-https/'=>'https://cn.wordpress.org/support/article/why-should-i-use-https/','Your site is not being fully served over a secure connection (using HTTPS).<br>As some AMP functionality requires a secure connection, you might experience degraded performance or broken components.<br><a href="%s">More details</a>'=>'无法通过安全连接(使用HTTPS)为您的网站提供完整的服务。<br>因为部分AMP功能需要安全连接, 所以您网站的性能可能会降低或者组件会受损。<br><a href="%s">更多详情</a>','Your server currently has the Xdebug PHP extension loaded. This can cause some of the AMP plugin\'s processes to timeout