rkers registered for the requested scope.'=>'没有针对请求的范围注册的 Service Worker。','Please update to PWA v0.2. Expected argument to be WP_Service_Worker_Scripts.'=>'请更新到PWA v0.2。参数应为WP_Service_Worker_Scripts。','Analytics entry for %1$s is missing one of the following keys: `%2$s` or `%3$s` (array keys: %4$s)'=>'%1$s的分析条目缺少以下键之一：`%2$s`或`%3$s`(数组键：%4$s)','AMP Project Contributors'=>'AMP项目贡献者','PHP-CSS-Parser is not available so CSS processing will not be available.'=>'PHP-CSS-Parser 不可用,因此无法进行 CSS 处理。','A conflicting version of PHP-CSS-Parser appears to be installed by another plugin or theme (located in %s). Because of this, CSS processing will be limited, and tree shaking will not be available.'=>'其他插件或主题(位于 %s 中)似乎安装了有冲突的 PHP-CSS-Parser 版本。因此,CSS 处理将受到限制,且 tree shaking 将不可用。','AMP CSS processing is limited because a conflicting version of PHP-CSS-Parser has been loaded by another plugin or theme. Tree shaking is not available.'=>'警告!其他插件或主题已加载有冲突的PHP-CSS-Parser版本,因此AMP CSS处理受限。Tree shaking不可用。','All AMP Validation Errors'=>'所有AMP验证错误','There is no amphtml version available for this URL.'=>'没有可用于此网址的 AMPHTML 版本。','It is not a best practice to use %1$s to load font CDN stylesheets. Please use %2$s to enqueue %3$s as its own separate script.'=>'使用 %1$s 加载字体 CDN 样式表不是最佳做法。请使用 %2$s 将 %3$s 加入队列, 作为其自有的独立脚本。','collapse child menu'=>'收起子菜单','expand child menu'=>'展开子菜单','Not Found (404)'=>'未找到 (404)','Search'=>'搜索','Date'=>'日期','Author'=>'作者','Blog'=>'博客','Homepage'=>'主页','Singular'=>'单数','Did not expect there to be more than one matching template. Did you filter %s to not honor the template hierarchy?'=>'没有预料到有多个匹配模板。是否对 %s 进行了过滤以便不遵从模板层次结构?','Supportable template "%s" does not have a callable callback.'=>'可支持的模板 "%s" 没有可调用的回调。','No WP_Query available.'=>'无可用的WP_Query。','An internal server error occurred when fetching the URL for validation.'=>'提取网址以进行验证时出现内部服务器错误。','The fetched URL was not found. It may have been deleted. If so, you can trash this.'=>'找不到提取的网址。该网址可能已被删除。如果已删除, 您可